        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThere is already a view here that will contain these jobs:\nhttps://github.com/onap/ci-management/blob/master/jjb/dcaegen2/dcaegen2.yaml#L2\n\nIs up to the teams if they want to create the new views for distributorapi and onboardingapi similar to how \"dcaegen2-platform-aoadapter\" appears in https://jenkins.onap.org/view/dcaegen2-platform-aoadapter/\n\nLet me know if this is the intention. If so, please +1",
