        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-12-11 19:17:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe intent is to have a common (new) view called \"dcaegen2-platform-mod\" and reference both distributorapi and onboardingapi jobs under it. The current template has unique view created, not sure how they should be linked. Will having common project-name under views (Line#6 on both yaml) establish this linkage?",
