        "timestamp": "2019-12-11 19:46:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nOh.. ok.. in that case, remove the view entry for one of these files. \nIn the other file that you choose to have the view, make it look like this:\n\n- project:\n    name: dcaegen2-platform-mod-project-view\n    project-name: dcaegen2-platform-mod\n    views:\n      - project-view",
